{
  "stem": "23942.3",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when I realized that he's not following me, I ran as fast as I could.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And where I was going to go, I had no idea.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I didn't know who is going to hide me, or who's going to give me, or who's going to protect me.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Till that day, all my life, I had somebody to watch over me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "First, my parents, my mother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Then, my grandmother always watched for me, and always took care of me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But it was the first time in my life that I realized-- I didn't even realize it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I just did the first step towards that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I took the step.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I walked away.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I ran.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I didn't-- like a wild, little animal.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I was so frightened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "If I didn't go completely out of my head that time, it's a miracle.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I should have been-- now, that-- from that night was the most scary night of my life, because it got dark soon.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I didn't know, really, where I was going.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I only remembered here and there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "My grandmother slept in different barns, and I didn't know where to-- even one of the place, I didn't even know how to-- really, how to get there.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But what I did was, I ran away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when I started running, first I ran towards the direction to-- there was a house not far.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she came out and she said, why are you running?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What's happening?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, I didn't answer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was afraid to answer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Later, I came back to that house, but I couldn't answer.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know, I was so frightened.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But then I went to a different-- I went to the opposite direction.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I went towards the direction where that little brook ran.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
